You can pass a variable to the `getTable` method to retrieve a table with a dynamic name.
```
import { SimpleDB } from "@nshiab/simple-data-analysis";
// We start a SimpleDB instance
const sdb = new SimpleDB();
// Define a variable for the table name
const tableName = "products";
// Retrieve the table using the variable
const products = await sdb.getTable(tableName);
// We close everything
await sdb.done();
```
